00:12:43,431 --> 00:12:44,171
thoughts about

224
00:12:44,672 --> 00:12:45,772
what you went through as a player

225
00:12:46,807 --> 00:12:47,248
in that game.

226
00:12:47,828 --> 00:12:51,751
So, last is, second to last, is a personal storytelling experience.

