234
00:13:19,962 --> 00:13:25,246
So my friends and I didn't have rule books, but I made up a pretend world, my friends made up characters

235
00:13:25,826 --> 00:13:29,048
and we rolled dice and told collaborative stories that are, it's still this...

236
00:13:29,548 --> 00:13:33,150
place of warmth and comfort where I feel like anything is possible when I think back at that time.

237
00:13:35,031 --> 00:13:38,733
So finally, of course, you need that focus on the central question of game narrative

